author: Huawei
description:
Huawei FusionSolar held The 5th Global Installer Summit in Dongguan, China, where more than 700 partners and installers from the European region gathered to explore PV and energy storage system (ESS) market trends, installer strategies, success stories, and marketing strategies. Together, we shaped a bright future for distributed energy! 💚

Watch the highlights to relive unforgettable moments from the summit and meet the best installers in the industry! 

🎥See you next year! ✨

#Huawei #HuaweiFusionSolar #GlobalInstallerSummit
